    <h2>2. Optimize for Performance</h2>
    <div class="project-box">
      <strong>Objective:</strong> Ensure the application runs efficiently and loads quickly.<br>
      <strong>Actions:</strong> Minimize CSS and JavaScript files, apply lazy loading for images, reduce the number of HTTP requests, and optimize load times.
    </div>
  </section>

